sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as React UI
    participant Nginx as Nginx
    participant AzureAD as Azure AD
    participant APIGateway as API Gateway
    participant BFF as BFF Layer
    participant JO as Journey Orchestrator
    participant RE as Rules Engine
    participant MS1 as Business Microservice 1
    participant MS2 as Business Microservice 2
    participant Caching  as Caching
    participant DB as Database
    participant IA as Integration Adapters
    participant EM as Event Messaging
    participant NS as Notification Service
    
    %% User Authentication Flow
    User->>UI: Access Application
    UI->>Nginx: HTTP Request
    Nginx->>AzureAD: Redirect for Authentication
    AzureAD->>User: Login Prompt
    User->>AzureAD: Credentials
    AzureAD->>AzureAD: Validate User
    AzureAD->>Nginx: Auth Token (JWT)
    Nginx->>UI: Auth Token + Redirect
    UI->>User: Display Dashboard
    
    %% Business Request Flow
    User->>UI: Initiate Business Action
    UI->>Nginx: API Request + Token
    Nginx->>APIGateway: Forward Request
    APIGateway->>APIGateway: Validate Token
    APIGateway->>BFF: Route to BFF
    
    %% BFF Processing
    BFF->>BFF: Aggregate Request Data
    BFF->>JO: Initiate Journey
    
    %% Journey Orchestration
    JO->>RE: Check Business Rules
    RE->>RE: Evaluate Rules
    RE->>JO: Rules Result
    
    %% Business Logic Execution
    JO->>MS1: Call Business Service 1
    MS1->>DB: Query Data
    DB->>MS1: Return Data
    MS1->>JO: Service 1 Response
    
    JO->>MS2: Call Business Service 2
    MS2->>IA: Call External System
    IA->>IA: Transform Data
    IA->>MS2: External Data
    MS2->>DB: Update Data
    DB->>MS2: Confirmation
    MS2->>JO: Service 2 Response
    
    %% Event Publishing
    JO->>EM: Publish Business Event
    EM->>NS: Trigger Notification
    NS->>User: Send Notification (Email/SMS)
    
    %% Response Flow
    JO->>BFF: Journey Complete
    BFF->>BFF: Transform Response
    BFF->>APIGateway: API Response
    APIGateway->>Nginx: Forward Response
    Nginx->>UI: HTTP Response
    UI->>User: Display Result
    
    %% Async Processing (parallel)
    par Async Event Processing
        EM->>MS1: Event Consumed
        MS1->>DB: Process Event
        EM->>MS2: Event Consumed
        MS2->>IA: Trigger Integration
    end